This is my first map, well the first one that didnt turn out like crap thats good enough to upload to the internet. I feel I did quite well in it, but some constructive criticism would be nice.

------
just your standard small aim map, dust themed and outdoors. Its functional , there are no known gameplay problems or bugs, I wouldent have uploaded it if there were.

If you like the map, please show love, by registering on www.gamerslife.dpclan.co.uk thank you.
